'''Trans Academy''' is a [[Special:MyLanguage/world|world]], [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]] community, and a non-profit 501(c)(3) charity organization, with a focus on education and inclusion towards VRChat's [[Wikipedia:Transgender|transgender]] and [[Wikipedia:LGBT|LGBTQIA+]] users and allies.

==Overview==
[[File:2024 03 29 Trans Lifeline Streamathon.png|thumb|A candid photo of the "Trans Lifeline Streamathon" event in 2024.]]
Founded in September of 2022 by ''Tizzy'', Trans Academy was created as a [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]] intended as a dedicated social outlet for transgender VRChat users. In November 2022, the 'Trans' group was created with the announcement of [[Groups]] in [[Open Beta]] to assign a designated group for Trans Academy. Groups originally had a capacity of 10,000 users, and the 'Trans' group had met the capacity limit<ref>[https://x.com/Tizzers/status/1629613761974915072 "10,000 members" posted by Tizzy on X.]</ref> until all groups received an [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202323 update in June of 2023] to be able to hold up to 100,000 users. In January of 2024, Trans Academy became recognized as a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization by the [[wikipedia:Internal_Revenue_Service|IRS]]<ref>[https://x.com/Tizzers/status/1744580387337339252 "granted 501(c)(3) Non-Profit status" posted by Tizzy on X.]</ref>.

==World==
Trans Academy was published to [[Community Labs]] on September 28, 2022 and hurdled over Labs on the same day. The design for the world was inspired by the 2013 anime '[[wikipedia:Little_Witch_Academia|Little Witch Academia]]'. The world has five primary hotspots: Spawn, the Square, the Café, the Stage, and the Ship.

=====Spawn=====
The spawn area provides resources in text, as well as teleportation buttons to the other hotspots of the world. There is also a [[Special:MyLanguage/Portals|portal]] to 'TA underground', a sister world that hosts music-related events for Trans Academy. Leading out of spawn, is a bridge that goes directly to the Square.

=====Square=====
The Square features a decorative fountain in the center, and paths leading to either the Stage on the right, or the Café on the left. [[wikipedia:Pride_flag|Pride flags]] of many types surround the Square.

=====Café=====
The Café is the primary hotspot where most users hang out. As the name implies, the café is a lounge with a coffee and espresso maker prefab; there are also couches, tables, a video player, a [[Special:MyLanguage/Mirrors|mirror]], and pens available. Walking past the café will lead to a beach, giving view to the Ship, and an inaccessible island. 

=====Stage=====
[[File:2024 03 31 Trans Day of Visibility .png|thumb|A speech, being given at the Trans Academy, for "Trans Day of Visibility 2024".]]
The Stage features a spacious pavillion and an outdoor amphitheatre that has a video player for presentations and seminars to be given during events.

=====Ship=====
The Ship is a colonial pirate ship that is isolated in the body of water not far from the beach. You can teleport to the Ship by clicking on a plush (''blåhaj'') shark outside of the Café, or by interacting with one of the teleportation buttons labeled 'Ship'.

